            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Atlassian Corporation - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TEAM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TEAM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TEAM-US</a>)截至台北時間01日21:30股價上漲14.58美元，報83.17美元，漲幅21.26%，成交量756,682（股），盤中最高價83.50美元、最低價83.17美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.36%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.53%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.89%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.26%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Atlassian Corporation - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TEAM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TEAM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TEAM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.43%</li> <li>近 1 月：+2.56%</li> <li>近 3 月：-41.96%</li> <li>近 6 月：-57.31%</li> <li>今年以來：-57.7%</li></ul></section></main>",
